    <abstract>
      <t>It is useful for routers in an OSPF routing domain to know the capabilities of their neighbors and other routers in the OSPFrouting domain. This draft proposes extensions to OSPF for advertising optional router capabilities. A new Router Information opaque LSA is proposed for this purpose.</t>
